OL,5, Water companies have been ordered to   
OL,6, pay back #114m to customers through    
OL,7, lower bills after missing key targets. 
OL,9,FOfwat, the industry regulator, said    
OL,10,Fthat firms are "falling short" on      
OL,11,Fperformance measures around leakages,  
OL,12,Fsupply and reducing pollution.         
OL,14,FIt said that following a review,       
OL,15,Fmillions of pounds would be returned to
OL,16,Fhouseholds by cutting bills.           
OL,18,FOfwat said in its assessment that not  
OL,19,Fone company reached the highest measure
OL,20,Fof performance.                        
